snippet.title: JoJo's Bizarre Adventure: All-Star Battle - Story Trailer (Part 1)
snippet.description:
JoJo's Bizarre Adventure All-Star Battle is available April 29, 2014 on the PSN for PlayStation 3 owners!

It is available as a physical product while supplies last at the following retailers-

Amazon: http://amzn.to/1ryCO72
Bandai Namco Games Store: http://bit.ly/1mT6Imc
